            . On the 20th of November I was walking down <placeName id="t18201206-84-crimeloc523">Fleet-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18201206-84-crimeloc523" type="placeName" value="Fleet-street"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18201206-84-crimeloc523" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18201206-84-off521 t18201206-84-crimeloc523"></join> about seven o'clock, about thirty yards from Temple-bar I felt somebody at my pocket. I turned round and saw the prisoner throw my handkerchief from his hand. I picked it up, collared him, and said,</p>

               <p>"You young rascal, why do you take the handkerchief from my pocket?" He said he did do it, but hoped I would forgive him. I gave him in custody to Prestige.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I am friendless and in distress. I should be thankful to be sent where they will do me good.</p>
